Usage: calculate_didt [-help] -net_name <string> -nworst <integer>
                      -state_directory <string>
                      [-window_steps <integer> | -window_size <float>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-net_name <string>            # net name (string, required)
-nworst <integer>             # top n largest value (int, required)
-state_directory <string>     # state directory (string, required)
-window_size <float>          # sliding window size (float, optional)
-window_steps <integer>       # sliding window steps (int, optional)